How This Calculator Works

Labor Savings

Calculated from hours automated × hourly rate × number of employees. Includes loaded costs (benefits, overhead).

Error Reduction

Assumes 80% reduction in errors from automation. Error cost includes time to fix plus any direct costs (rework, penalties, etc.).

Investment

One-time costs (software, services, training) plus ongoing annual maintenance and support.

Note: Results are estimates. Actual savings depend on implementation quality, user adoption, and process specifics. Contact us for a detailed workflow analysis.
